		= FEATURES
		> Namespaces
		- added new Namespace object class and ZMI forms

		> MetadataAware
		- adds namespace information to user metadata
		- use site domain for record id
		- created method to setup metadata dictionary, used by other classes too

		> ZCatalogHarvester
		- changed when adding oai_state to portal catalog
		- properly creates multiple records for documents with multiple metadata
		- use site domain for record id
		- cleaned up manual_publish area
		- now harvester doesn't delete oai_status index in portal catalog

		> Repository
		- added code to access new Namespace classes-
		- added access/set method for the repositories domain name
		- moved misc zoai information to Preferences tab, changed manage methods
		- moved zoai site admin and name to preferences
		  in preparation for rebuilding data if anything in Info tab changes

		> site domain
		- moved site domain for record id to ZMI, not hard-coded
		- added to ZMI gui


		= BUGS
		- fixed searching problem with portal catalog, removed hack
		- changed method parameters in dtml to access metadata

		= MISCELLANEOUS
		- manual publishing looks for shared documents all of the time
		- filter objects from ZMI drop down that users shouldn't add
		- cleaned up 'zoai' object access (works anywhere- groups, root, etc)
		- changed Daily, Weekly, Monthly minute values in dtml to real numbers
		- changed ZMI text for Zope OAI Server Prefs form
		- added links to metadata schemas  and more user info when in portal
		  adding metadata to documents. allows users to pre-validate their metadata
		- search for 'oai_dc' metadata and not 'dc'

